{"tid":2320882,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李嘉誠扶植諾獎得主 再暗諷林鄭：今天的領導不可再自我中心","createTime":"2020-12-11T06:47:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T10:39:36.000Z","uid":130626,"like":41,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2f569478275aab1ba75b05790186821d2f3134f3","tid":2320882,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T06:47:33.000Z","msg":"長和系資深顧問李嘉誠近年透過基金會扶植不少科學家，他今早以視像形式出席諾貝爾獎祝賀儀式時，向諾貝爾醫學獎得主的兩名團隊成員贈予同等獎金，並對得獎者期望同儕得到認可的態度表示讚賞，稱無私的本心是最難能可貴的，因 「今天的領導不可再以自我為中心」，似是呼應其「紅顏知己」周凱旋早前評林鄭班子的言論。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201211/AWNBJNXQH5DIPNZDUDK2KZ4TDE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201211%2FAWNBJNXQH5DIPNZDUDK2KZ4TDE%2F&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2Wrppvqcls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=f640f6dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201211%2FAWNBJNXQH5DIPNZDUDK2KZ4TDE%2F&h=92a08e9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201211/AWNBJNXQH5DIPNZDUDK2KZ4TDE/</a>"},{"pid":"da3ee96ece5d66ca113b88ddc5f43223a3b59d67","tid":2320882,"uid":154373,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T06:48:37.000Z","msg":"又屈黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5681c2a71d9d1c4619ea7180c430b6f39136e5d1","tid":2320882,"uid":269527,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T07:44:52.000Z","msg":"我覺得係明諷，唔係暗諷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99c8cbe3ee09c7a9fe5e6f5cd796976aff3b04aa","tid":2320882,"uid":155095,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T07:48:18.000Z","msg":"其實佢唔係話緊林鄭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xi6a0jz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxi6a0jz.jpg&h=f38e175b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ntdtv.com/assets/